## CSS & Design System Guidelines
### Architecture & Structure
- Adopt `@layer reset, base, components, utilities, overrides;` in `src/styles/global.css`
- **Global CSS** (`global.css`, `terminal.css`): Base resets, tokens, typography, layout utilities
- **Scoped CSS**: Component-specific styles only. Use `:global()` sparingly and only when targeting 3rd-party UI (e.g., Pagefind, Shiki)
- **Never use `!important`** except for unavoidable 3rd-party overrides. Prefer specificity control or `:where()`

### Design Tokens (Mandatory)
All values must be tokenized in `:root`. Never hardcode colors, spacing, radii, or shadows.
```css
:root {
  /* Colors */
  --brand-color: #4b63c5;
  --accent-color: #7e9ddc;
  --font-color: #232748;
  --font-color-light: #5d5d5d;
  --bg-color: #f2f5fc;
  --card-bg-color: #ffffff;
  --card-border-color: #e2e9f7;
  --shadow-color: rgba(75, 99, 197, 0.08);
  --shadow-hover-color: rgba(75, 99, 197, 0.15);
  
  /* Semantic */
  --success-color: #10b981;
  --warning-color: #f59e0b;
  --danger-color: #ef4444;
  
  /* Typography */
  --font-sans: 'Prompt', system-ui, sans-serif;
  --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  --text-xs: clamp(0.75rem, 0.7rem + 0.2vw, 0.8rem);
  --text-sm: clamp(0.875rem, 0.85rem + 0.2vw, 0.95rem);
  --text-base: clamp(1rem, 0.95rem + 0.3vw, 1.125rem);
  --text-lg: clamp(1.125rem, 1.05rem + 0.4vw, 1.3rem);
  --text-xl: clamp(1.25rem, 1.15rem + 0.6vw, 1.6rem);
  --text-2xl: clamp(1.5rem, 1.35rem + 0.8vw, 2rem);
  --text-3xl: clamp(1.875rem, 1.65rem + 1.2vw, 2.75rem);
  
  /* Spacing & Radii */
  --space-1: 0.25rem; --space-2: 0.5rem; --space-3: 0.75rem;
  --space-4: 1rem; --space-5: 1.25rem; --space-6: 1.5rem;
  --space-8: 2rem; --space-10: 2.5rem; --space-12: 3rem;
  --radius-sm: 8px; --radius-md: 12px; --radius-lg: 16px; --radius-xl: 20px;
  --radius-full: 9999px;
}
```

### Typography Hierarchy (Critical)
- `h1` â†’ `--text-3xl`, `h2` â†’ `--text-2xl`, `h3` â†’ `--text-xl`, `h4` â†’ `--text-lg`
- Body `p`, `li` â†’ `--text-base` or `--text-sm`
- Always use `line-height: 1.3`â€“`1.6` contextually
- **Never** set `h1, h2, h3 { font-size: 1rem; }`

### Component Deduplication
- Extract shared card styles into a base `.card` class:
  ```css
  .card {
    background: var(--card-bg-color);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border-color);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px var(--shadow-color);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px var(--shadow-hover-color);
    border-color: var(--brand-color);
  }
  ```
- Specific cards (`.blog-card`, `.tool-card`, `.category-card`, `.feature-card`) must **extend** `.card` and only override layout/content differences.

### Breakpoints & Responsive Strategy
- Mobile-first. Standard breakpoints:
  ```css
  @media (min-width: 640px) { /* sm */ }
  @media (min-width: 768px) { /* md */ }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { /* lg */ }
  @media (min-width: 1280px) { /* xl */ }
  ```
- Never use arbitrary pixel values (`400px`, `900px`) without token justification.

