## Accessibility & Performance Standards
- âś… **Focus States**: Always use `:focus-visible` with `outline` or `box-shadow`
- âś… **Motion**: Wrap all transitions/animations in `@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)`
- âś… **Contrast**: Maintain â‰Ą 4.5:1 for body text, â‰Ą 3:1 for large text/UI components
- âś… **Fonts**: Replace `@import` in CSS with `<link rel="preload" as="style">` in `<head>` to eliminate render-blocking
- âś… **Images**: Always include `width`, `height`, `loading="lazy"`, `decoding="async"`, and descriptive `alt`
- âś… **Shiki/Terminal**: Remove `.prose pre.shiki { background: unset !important; }`. Use `@layer` specificity or `:where(.shiki)` instead.

